Fund Reports ​

This module is used to submit, review, and approve fund reports.

INFO

Make sure to add /api prefix in the API endpoint.

Get Fund Reports Index Endpoint ​

http
GET /reports
GET /reports

Headers ​

  • Content-Type: application/json
  • Authorization: Bearer {token}

Query Parameter ​

NameTypeDescriptionNullable
pageintPage numberfalse
search_machineintSearch by machine idtrue
search_answerintSearch by fund report status idtrue
search_shift_start_atstringSearch by shift start attrue
search_shift_end_atstringSearch by shift end attrue
search_shiftintSearch by shift idtrue
search_per_pageintSearch by per pagetrue
is_full_pageintIs full pagetrue
is_group_by_machineintIs group by machinetrue
order_columnstringOrder by columntrue
order_directionstringOrder by directiontrue
